IMAPAccount josemotanet
Host imap.fastmail.com
User jose@josemota.net
PassCmd "echo $MAIL_PASSWORD_JOSEMOTANET"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore josemotanet-remote
Account josemotanet

MaildirStore josemotanet-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/mail/josemotanet/
Inbox ~/mail/josemotanet/Inbox

Channel josemotanet
Master :josemotanet-remote:
Slave :josemotanet-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
